data.title: What are the hardest adjustments to make when visiting Algeria?
data.meta_description: Answer: I think that what is hard for someone, can be peanut for another, depending where you are coming from. All is relative. I come from Algeria, lived there the 8 first years of my life, then moved to Europe. I still visit the country from time to time and although it is changing very quickly...
